		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/古岩龙蜥%B7溟冬.assets/Image_7.png')" x="1392" y="362">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/古岩龙蜥%B7溟冬.assets/Image_8.png')" x="1393" y="842">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/古岩龙蜥%B7溟冬.assets/Image_9.png')" x="1392" y="585">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/古岩龙蜥%B7溟冬.assets/Image_10.png')" x="1392" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/古岩龙蜥%B7溟冬.assets/Image_11.png')" x="596" y="619" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/古岩龙蜥%B7溟冬.assets/Image_12.png')" x="576" y="598" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="424" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">古岩龙蜥凝聚自身元素之力，朝地面喷射，造成大范围对应元素的<span color="#99e5ff">200%</span><span>伤害。若角色受护盾庇护则只受到对应元素的</span><span color="#99e5ff">40%</span><span>伤害。<br/>该技能可被</span><span textDecoration="underline">盾反</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/古岩龙蜥%B7溟冬.assets/Image_13.png')" x="720" y="842">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="66" y="1128" width="435" height="97" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">出场时额外获得<span color="#ffbfbf">100%</span><span>对应元素的常驻抗性。出场默认冰属性，技能会在冰水两个属性间转换。<br/>盾反：护盾必须能扛住该次攻击，方可触发盾反，盾反成功后古岩龙蜥虚弱6s。若盾反成功，则削减全抗性，并</span><span color="#ffebbf">扣除10%生命值(异元素盾为3%)</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
